---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = 'Privacy Policy | wrongfuldeathcalc.com';
const description = 'How wrongfuldeathcalc.com handles visitor information, cookies, analytics, and advertising data.';
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><em>Last updated: May 2026.</em></p>

  <p>This page explains what information we collect when you use wrongfuldeathcalc.com, how we use it, and your choices. Compliance posture is GDPR + CCPA where applicable.</p>

  <h2>What we collect</h2>

  <h3>What you give us directly</h3>
  <p>What you send us. If you email <a href="mailto:hey@theclicklab.agency">hey@theclicklab.agency</a> we receive your email address and message contents. We have no user accounts, signup forms, or comment sections.</p>

  <h3>What the calculator does</h3>
  <p>The settlement calculator runs entirely in your browser. Numbers you enter are not sent to our server, not stored, not logged, and not transmitted to any third party. Close the tab and they are gone.</p>

  <h3>Server logs and analytics</h3>
  <p>Our hosting provider records standard access logs (IP, request URL, user agent, timestamp) for reliability and security. We may use a privacy-respecting analytics tool to count page views; we do not build behavioral profiles.</p>

  <h3>Advertising</h3>
  <p>This site shows ads through Google AdSense. Google and its partners use cookies to serve ads based on prior visits. Opt out at <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a> or <a href="https://www.aboutads.info" rel="noopener">aboutads.info</a>. EU/EEA/UK visitors see AdSense's <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" rel="noopener">partner site policy</a>.</p>

  <h2>How we use what we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Email you send us:</strong> to respond. We don't add you to a mailing list and don't share it.</li>
    <li><strong>Server logs:</strong> security, abuse prevention, debugging.</li>
    <li><strong>Advertising cookies:</strong> set by Google and ad partners, not by us. We don't see who you are individually.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What we don't do</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Sell visitor information. No lead-generation, no attorney lead sales.</li>
    <li>Track you for case intake. Calculator inputs stay in your browser.</li>
    <li>Maintain user accounts.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Your choices</h2>
  <p>Block third-party cookies in your browser to limit AdSense personalization. The site works fine with cookies blocked. <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" rel="noopener">Google Ads Settings</a> lets you turn off personalized advertising specifically.</p>
  <p>For GDPR/UK GDPR or CCPA rights, email <a href="mailto:hey@theclicklab.agency">hey@theclicklab.agency</a> with subject <code>[PRIVACY REQUEST]</code>.</p>

  <h2>Children</h2>
  <p>This site is not directed at children under 16 and we don't knowingly collect their information.</p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>If we materially change data handling, this page and the "last updated" date will update.</p>

  <h2>Contact about privacy</h2>
  <p><a href="mailto:hey@theclicklab.agency">hey@theclicklab.agency</a>, subject <code>[PRIVACY]</code>.</p>
</BaseLayout>
